						<summary>

						<p>On the wall of the east inner <hi rend="italic">gōpura,</hi> Śvētāraṇyēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Year 10: 981 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This records a gift of twenty-five <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tiruveṇkāḍu-dēvar by Vaṉṉāḍ-uḍaiyār Maṟa-nāṭṭu vēḷār. The <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> undertook to protect the gift (See No. 75 dealt with below).</p>						

						<p>Published in <hi rend="italic">S.I.I.,</hi> Vol. XIX No. 255.</p>						

						</summary>
